name: .SNZ File Extension
summary: Learn about .SNZ files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can use Snappy (cross-platform) to decompress SNZ files. However, because Snappy is a source code library, typical PC users may have trouble using Snappy to decompress SNZ files. Snzip, a cross-platform compression and decompression tool based on Snappy, can help users decompress SNZ files. Before you can use Snzip, you must install Snappy.
